{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"AesCbcParams","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/AesCbcParams","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Crypto_API\">Web Crypto API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/AesCbcParams\"><code>AesCbcParams</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Web Crypto API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Crypto\"><code>Crypto</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CryptoKey\"><code>CryptoKey</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto\"><code>SubtleCrypto</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/crypto_property\"><code>crypto_property</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Das <strong><code>AesCbcParams</code></strong>&nbsp;Verzeichnis (dictionary) der&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Crypto_API\">Web Crypto API </a>wird als&nbsp;<code>algorithm</code>&nbsp;Parameter an die Funktionen <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/encrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.encrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/decrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.decrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>,&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/wrapKey\"><code>SubtleCrypto.wrapKey()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/unwrapKey\"><code>SubtleCrypto.unwrapKey()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> übergeben, wenn der Algorithmus&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/encrypt#aes-cbc\">AES-CBC</a>&nbsp;verwendet wird.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n <dd>A <a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a>. Der Wert sollte auf&nbsp;<code>AES-CBC</code>&nbsp;gesetzt werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"iv\"><code>iv</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>BufferSource</code></a>. Der Initialisierungsvektor. Er muss 16 Bytes lang sein und sollte unvorhersehbar und am besten kryptografisch zufällig sein. Er muss aber nicht geheim sein, er kann unverschlüsselt mit dem Kryptogram übertragen werden.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Siehe Beispiele für <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/encrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.encrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/decrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.decrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/WebCryptoAPI/#dfn-AesCbcParams\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Cryptography API<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'SubtleCrypto.AesCbcParams' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibilität","title":"Browser Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Browser&nbsp;mit Unterstützung für den \"AES-CBC\" Algorithmus werden die Methoden <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/encrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.encrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/decrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.decrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>,&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/wrapKey\"><code>SubtleCrypto.wrapKey()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/unwrapKey\"><code>SubtleCrypto.unwrapKey()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> für diesen Typ unterstützen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>CBC Modus wird in Sektion 6.2 des&nbsp;<a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://nvlpubs.nist.gov/nistpubs/Legacy/SP/nistspecialpublication800-38a.pdf#%5B%7B%22num%22%3A70%2C%22gen%22%3A0%7D%2C%7B%22name%22%3A%22Fit%22%7D%5D\" rel=\"noopener\">NIST SP800-38A standard</a>&nbsp;spezifiziert.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/encrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.encrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/decrypt\"><code>SubtleCrypto.decrypt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/wrapKey\"><code>SubtleCrypto.wrapKey()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/unwrapKey\"><code>SubtleCrypto.unwrapKey()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das AesCbcParams Verzeichnis (dictionary) der Web Crypto API wird als algorithm Parameter an die Funktionen SubtleCrypto.encrypt() (en-US), SubtleCrypto.decrypt() (en-US), SubtleCrypto.wrapKey() (en-US) und SubtleCrypto.unwrapKey() (en-US) übergeben, wenn der Algorithmus AES-CBC verwendet wird.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AesCbcParams","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/aescbcparams","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/aescbcparams/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/AesCbcParams","title":"AesCbcParams"}],"pageTitle":"AesCbcParams - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}